                .text-center   Privacy Notice
                br
                |   This privacy notice discloses the privacy practices for DataJoint.io. This privacy notice applies solely to information collected by DataJoint.io. It will notify you of the following:
                br
                |   &emsp; 1. What personally identifiable information is collected from you through the website, how it is used and with whom it may be shared.
